official_title: A resolution relative to the election of Members to the Committee on Rules.

summary.text: Elects the following named Members to the Committee on Rules: Ray J. Madden, Indiana, Chairman; James J. Delaney of New York; Richard Bolling of Missouri; Thomas P. O'Neill, Jr., of Massachusetts; B. F. Sisk of California; John Young of Texas; Claude Pepper of Florida, and Spark M. Matsunaga of Hawaii.
